agree to be bound by the terms of this License.

The purpose of this License is to make the Software freely available to
attorneys and organizations who primarily represent consumers, plaintiffs, and
individuals in civil litigation, while requiring a separate written license
agreement for use by those who primarily defend institutional interests against
such individuals.

